{% endblock meta-tags %}
 
{% block body-tag-classes %}mz-visit-us mz-w-snackbar{% endblock body-tag-classes %} 
{% block body-content %}
<section>
    <article>
        <h1 class="mz-pagetitle">Chocolate Shoppe and Fudge Counter</h1>
        <figure class="vertImage">
            <img src="/resources/images/visit-us/CA_chocolate_shop.jpg">
        </figure>
        <p>
            Located in the Visitor Center, our Chocolate Shoppe is a chocolate lover's dream! Watch candy chefs create gourmet hand-made confections like dark and milk chocolate candy clusters, 
            decadent truffles and fudge in a variety of standard and seasonal flavors. And that's not all!
        </p>
        <p>
            Specialties of the Chocolate Shoppe include freshly-made marshmallow treats, gourmet caramel apples, caramel corn and seasonal chocolate molds such as chocolate bunnies at Easter or a 
            chocolate Santa Claus during Christmas!
        </p>
        <p>
            Stop at our fudge counter to try free samples of our delicious fudge. Our specialties include Cookies &amp; Cream and Red Velvet fudge.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="http://content.jellybelly.com/cachefly/Jelly-Belly/Downloads/chocolate_shop_items_2014.pdf" target="_blank">Click here</a> to see all the items that the Chocolate Shoppe offers.
        </p>
        <p class="finePrint">
            ALLERGEN NOTICE: Our Retail Store, Caf√©, and Chocolate Shoppe confections and foods contain certain allergy triggers. Please check out our <a href="/frequently-asked-questions">FAQ</a> (Frequently Asked Questions) to learn more about allergens and to submit a question. 
        </p>
    </article>
</section>
{% endblock body-content %}





